{
  "title": "Take a tour inside Zsa Zsa Gabor's former Palm Springs retreat — it's for sale!",
  "content": "<div><div class=\"article-body__content article-body-font--loading\"><p class=\"\">“I am a marvelous housekeeper. Every time I leave a man, I keep his house,” Zsa Zsa Gabor famously said.</p><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183917/zsa-zsa-living-room-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183917/zsa-zsa-living-room-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183917/zsa-zsa-living-room-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183917/zsa-zsa-living-room-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183917/zsa-zsa-living-room-2-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\">The actress with the long eyelashes and the distinct Hungarian accent died this week, but her spirit lives in timeless quotes — and homes — like this mid-century modern in Palm Springs.</p><section class=\"inline-video inline-video--in-body\"><div class=\"inline-video__background\"><div class=\"inline-video__player\"><div class=\"videoPlayer styles_videoPlayer__hWpgx styles_adNotPlaying__yQRQY\"><div class=\"videoSlate\"><div class=\"expiredOverlay items-center df absolute w-100 h-100 z-2 f7 f8-m\"><div class=\"expiredText founders-cond tc w-100 gray-60\">We apologize, this video has expired.</div></div><a href=\"https://www.today.com/video/zsa-zsa-gabor-dies-at-99-fans-friends-remember-colorful-actress-836534339758\" class=\"allowClicksOnPreview\"><picture class=\"\"><source srcset=\"https://media3.s-nbcnews.com/j/MSNBC/Components/Video/201612/tdy_miguel_gabor_161219.focal-860x484.jpg\"><source srcset=\"https://media3.s-nbcnews.com/j/MSNBC/Components/Video/201612/tdy_miguel_gabor_161219.focal-1000x563.jpg\"><img src=\"https://media3.s-nbcnews.com/j/MSNBC/Components/Video/201612/tdy_miguel_gabor_161219.focal-760x428.jpg\"></picture></a></div></div></div></div></section><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183918/zsa-zsa-living-rom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183918/zsa-zsa-living-rom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183918/zsa-zsa-living-rom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183918/zsa-zsa-living-rom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183918/zsa-zsa-living-rom-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.zillow.com/homedetails/19-Cahuilla-Hills-Dr-Palm-Springs-CA-92264/18032360_zpid/\">The $969,000 listing </a>says Gabor lived here, but it’s not clear whether the home was her own purchase (or rental), or acquired from one of her seven divorces.</p><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183920/zsa-zsa-kitchen-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183920/zsa-zsa-kitchen-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183920/zsa-zsa-kitchen-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183920/zsa-zsa-kitchen-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183920/zsa-zsa-kitchen-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"><strong>RELATED: <a href=\"http://www.today.com/home/pat-benatar-lists-maui-home-see-inside-t105037\">Pat Benatar is moving on from her gorgeous Maui home — see inside!</a></strong></p><p class=\"\">What is clear is that she, like other Palm Springs celebs from <a href=\"http://www.zillow.com/blog/disney-home-now-for-sale-208903/\">Walt Disney</a> to <a href=\"http://www.zillow.com/blog/rent-dicaprio-mid-century-modern-171284/\">Leonardo DiCaprio</a>, knew how to live it up in the desert.</p><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183921/zsa-zsa-bedroom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183921/zsa-zsa-bedroom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183921/zsa-zsa-bedroom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183921/zsa-zsa-bedroom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183921/zsa-zsa-bedroom-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\">Like any pure <a href=\"http://www.zillow.com/blog/mid-century-modern/#organic\">mid-century modern</a>, the 1958 home features an open floor plan and walls of windows. The views are desert spectacular: a blend of cacti, palm trees and mountains — plus the stunning swimming pool just outside the door.</p><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183930/zsa-zsa-bedroom-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183930/zsa-zsa-bedroom-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183930/zsa-zsa-bedroom-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183930/zsa-zsa-bedroom-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183930/zsa-zsa-bedroom-2-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183931/zsa-zsa-bathroom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183931/zsa-zsa-bathroom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183931/zsa-zsa-bathroom-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183931/zsa-zsa-bathroom-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183931/zsa-zsa-bathroom-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\">The small compound’s 1,800 square feet include a main house and a guesthouse with its own kitchenette and pool views.</p><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183933/zsa-zsa-pool-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183933/zsa-zsa-pool-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183933/zsa-zsa-pool-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183933/zsa-zsa-pool-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183933/zsa-zsa-pool-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"inline-image inline-image--medium inline-image--no-caption\"><picture class=\"inline-image__image\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1120w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183934/zsa-zsa-pool-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-560w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183934/zsa-zsa-pool-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><source srcset=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-1520w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183934/zsa-zsa-pool-2-today-161222.jpg 2x, https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183934/zsa-zsa-pool-2-today-161222.jpg 1x\"><img src=\"https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit-760w,f_auto,q_auto:best/newscms/2016_51/1183934/zsa-zsa-pool-2-today-161222.jpg\" alt=\"Zsa Zsa Gabor's Palm Springs home\" width=\"1024\"></picture><figcaption class=\"caption inline-image__caption\"><span class=\"caption__container\"></span><span class=\"caption__source\">Courtesy of Zillow</span></figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"><strong>RELATED:<a href=\"http://www.today.com/home/bob-hope-s-palm-springs-home-sells-under-asking-t105096\"> Just sold! Peek inside the Palm Springs pad that Bob Hope once called home</a></strong></p><p class=\"\">The listing agents are TTK Represents from <a href=\"http://www.ttkrepresents.com/19-Cahuilla-Hills-Drive\">HK Lane/Christie’s International Real Estate</a>. Hat tip to <a href=\"http://www.curbed.com/2016/12/19/14005976/zsa-zsa-gabor-palm-springs-midcentury-modern-homes-for-sale\">Curbed</a> for the timely find.</p><p class=\"\">Related:</p></div></div>",
